profile:
McLaren Architectural Designs is a local architectural designs and drafting service. We specialize in designs for residential projects but can also do small commercial buildings up to 6400 square feet. We provide design ideas to help you put your ideas to paper to start making you project a reality. We provide the following drafting services:

- Custom home drawings
- Small Commercial Buildings
- Carports and Garages
- Decks and Sheds
- Additions and renovations
- Change of use drawings
- Agricultural Buildings

If you are in need of drawings for a permit please give us a call and we would be happy to help you get started. We are fully insured and registered with the Ministry of Municipal Affairs and Housing. We are BCIN qualified in small buildings.
